    "name": "I'm a cowboy: Western Shooter",
    "steam_appid": 1712120,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712120/extras/231a7fd383ab193aaa96e39a7abde10c.avif?t=1687178015\" width=600 height=334 /></span><br><br>Billy the Kid, now Mister World 1895, used to be your friend, but that all changed after you left the gang. And on one of the ill-fated days of 1898, Kid and his friends broke into your house to get even for old grievances.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712120/extras/3b983189f90508b6916d983391a108bf.avif?t=1687178015\" width=600 height=334 /></span><br><br>In vain your wife opened the door, now she is dead, and you have nothing left that could keep you from returning to the path of pain and murder.<br><br><strong>Grab your revolver, spur your horse and prove to all the thugs that you are the best shooter in the entire Wild West!</strong><br><br>You are waiting for exciting adventures, dynamic skirmishes, duels and the opportunity to improve the characteristics of the hero.<br><br>- 10 unique levels;<br>- Horse riding;<br>- Colorful shooting;<br>- Duels;<br>- Improving the characteristics of the character;<br>- Dramatic story.<br><br><strong>The game also has a zombie mode.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712120/extras/ff2377ef11761942eb85e359db908d34.avif?t=1687178015\" width=600 height=334 /></span>",
